install git: sudo apt-get install git
install node.js: sudo apt-get install nodejs
install npm: sudo apt-get install npm
update npm: sudo npm install -g npm@latest
install pm2: sudo npm install -g pm2@latest

git clone https://github.com/imasianxd/WS2812Controller.git

ensure ws2812b connection is made to pin 18, +5V and GND of pi
change # of led in strip.js
change to port number in app.js 

cd into folder and run sudo npm rebuild
crontab -e as su, enter @reboot pm2 start /path/to/script/app.js
